launcher.title: Send custom message
launcher.description: As a developer you can send messages to your functions.

infohub_trigger.YOU_AS_A_DEVELOPER_CAN_SEND_A_MESSAGE_TO: You as a developer can send a message to your emerging plugin.
infohub_trigger.SELECT_THE_NODE_YOU_WANT_TO_SEND_THE_MES: Select the node you want to send the message to
infohub_trigger.SELECT_THE_PLUGIN_YOU_WANT_TO_SEND_THE_M: Select the plugin you want to send the message to
infohub_trigger.SELECT_THE_FUNCTION_YOU_WANT_TO_SEND_THE: Select the function you want to send the message to
infohub_trigger.DEFAULT_MESSAGE_FOR_THE_SELECTED_FUNCTIO: Default message for the selected function
infohub_trigger.THIS_IS_THE_MESSAGE_YOU_CAN_SEND_TO_THE_: This is the message you can send to the selected plugin.
infohub_trigger.THE_MESSAGE_YOU_SEE_IS_THE_DEFAULT_VALUE: The message you see is the default values the function have set.
infohub_trigger.HERE_YOU_WILL_SEE_THE_RESPONSE_FROM_THE_: Here you will see the response from the function.
